	<term>MyStyle <emphasis remap='I'>"style_name"</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Specifies a MyStyle definition (which covers text and/or gradients and/or background pixmaps),
		which can later be reused and is covered in the MyStyle section of the documentation.</para>
		<para>See Also: <ulink url="MyStyle#synopsis">MyStyle definition</ulink> for further details.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
